org.junit.gen5.engine.junit5.descriptor

Class NestedClassTestDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.gen5.engine.support.descriptor.AbstractTestDescriptor
      • org.junit.gen5.engine.junit5.descriptor.JUnit5TestDescriptor
        • org.junit.gen5.engine.junit5.descriptor.ClassTestDescriptor
          • org.junit.gen5.engine.junit5.descriptor.NestedClassTestDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Node<JUnit5EngineExecutionContext>, TestDescriptor

    @API(value=Internal)
public class NestedClassTestDescriptor
extends ClassTestDescriptor
    TestDescriptor for tests based on nested (but not static) Java classes.

    Default Display Names

    The default display name for a non-static nested test class is the simple name of the class.

    5.0
